'''隆背張口蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Chasmagnathus convexus'''''}}），亦作'''隆脊張口蟹'''，是一種在[[東亞|東亞]]的[[特有種|特有種]]，常見於[[乾潟|乾潟]]，屬於[[方蟹總科|方蟹總科]]的[[弓蟹科|弓蟹科]]，分布於北至[[日本|日]][[大韓民國|韓]]、南至[[越南|越南]]北部<ref name=Shih2008>{{cite journal |author=[[施習德|Hsi-Te Shih]] & Hiroshi Suzuki | year = 2008 | title = Taxonomy, phylogeny, and biogeography of the endemic mudflat crab ''Helice''/''Chasmagnathus'' complex (Crustacea: Brachyura: Varunidae) from East Asia | journal = [[Zoological_Studies|Zoological Studies]] | volume = 47 | issue = 1 | pages=114–125 | url=http://zoolstud.sinica.edu.tw/Journals/47.1/114.pdf |language=en }}</ref><ref name="MSIP">{{cite web |url=http://species-identification.org/species.php?species_group=crabs_of_japan&id=1734&menuentry=soorten |title=''Chasmagnathus convexus'' |format= |work=Crabs of Japan |editor=Katsushi Sakai |accessdate=2009-01-16 |language=en }}</ref>。在日本及台灣，本物種又稱作「濱蟹」。

本物種有兩個不同的形式，主要是顏色的分別：有[[橄欖綠|橄欖綠]]及紫色兩種<ref name=Shih2008/>。這個分別相信是因為食性的分別而造成。與其他物種相比，本物種的尺寸算是比較大。其[[頭胸甲|頭胸甲]]有{{convert|4.5|to|5|cm|in}}闊<ref name=Miyasaka2007>{{cite journal | author = Hitoshi Miyasaka, Motomi Genkai-Kato, Yukiko Goda & Koji Omori | year = 2007 | title = Length-weight relationships of two varunid crab species, ''Helice tridens'' and ''Chasmagnathus convexus'', in Japan | journal = [[Limnology_(journal)|Limnology]] | volume = 8 | issue = 1 | pages = 81–83 | doi = 10.1007/s10201-006-0195-8 | url = http://www.springerlink.com/index/106745J4158020N3.pdf }}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，橫長近圓形<ref>{{cite web |url=http://catalog.digitalarchives.tw/item/00/03/30/33.html |title=隆背張口蟹(Chasmagnathus convexus) |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2014-08-18 |publisher=[[數位典藏與數位學習聯合目錄|數位典藏與數位學習聯合目錄]]}}</ref>。本物種主要是[[夜行性|夜行性]]<ref name=Shih2008/>。

